original_title: Jukebox Saturday Night: Sounds Of The 60's
overview: This rare collection of videos hosted by the legendary radio DJ Ken Sparkes; Jukebox Saturday Night plays many never before seen music video clips from the greatest artists of our time. Most of the songs featured were previously only “heard” on radio, but, they have searched around and found the video clips for them, putting a face to the performers.
title: Jukebox Saturday Night: Sounds Of The 60's
